PrecisAppointment of STEPHEN BRERETON as Consul General of Canada at Buffalo, United States of America; MARCY GROSSMAN as Consul General of Canada at Miami, United States of America; MARGARET HUBER as Consul General of Canada at Milan, Italian Republic; JEAN-YVES DIONNE as Consul General of Canada at Rio de Janeiro, Federative Republic of Brazil; MARC LEPAGE as Consul General of Canada at San Francisco/San Jose, United States of America; JEAN-MARC DUVAL as Consul General of Canada at Sao Paulo, Federative Republic of Brazil; CHRISTOPHER BROWN as Consul General of Canada at Cape Town, Republic of South Africa; YVES BOULANGER as Ambassador of Canada to the Federal Democratic Republic of Ethiopia; MATTHEW LEVIN as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Colombia; ANNE-MARIE BOURCIER as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Finland; CLAIRE POULIN as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Latvia, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Lithuania; and JILLIAN STIRK as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Norway.
